data.Name: LILHUDDY
data.Bio: Cole Chase Hudson, better known by Lil Huddy, is a rising TikTok star. He was born on the 15th of May in 2002 in Stockton, California. He is a co-founder of the highly successful Hype House and has been well known for his public relationship with Charli D'amelio, as well as popularising the "e-boy" style. Beginning his music career in January 2021, Hudson signed to Interscope Records to release his debut single 21st Century Vampire, after featuring in a Machine Gun Kelly film. Read more on Last.fm
